<%= provide(:title, "Services") %>
<% content_for :head do %>
	<meta name="description" content:"Color Craze specializes in marketing materials for small and medium businesses and other organizations.">
	<meta name="keywords" content:"digital printing, frisco, plano, mckinney, allen, fliers, brochures, postcards, business cards, booklets, directories, notecards, posters, letterhead, envelopes, programs, tickets, sunday school lessons, multi-part forms, coloring pages, planograms, manuals, bookmarks, product labels, bulletins, invitations, greeting cards, calendars">
<% end %>

<div class="row">
	<div class="large-12 columns">
		<h1>Printing Services</h1>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="thinSpacerRow"></div>
<div class="row prodDesc">
	<div class="large-3 columns">
		<h2>Business Cards</h2>
		<div class="productBoxImg"><%= image_tag("bus_card2.jpg") %></div>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<div class="prodDescBox">
			<p>When you meet a potential customer, employee, vendor or parter, the first impression you make is entirely up to you. But part of that impression - the only lasting, tangible part - is your business card. We take the care to consistently produce cards you'll be proud to share.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Single- or double-sided</li>
				<li>Card weight up to XX</li>
				<li>Matte to glossy finish</li>
				<li>Lots sizes from 100 to 5,000</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="thinSpacerRow"></div>
<div class="row prodDesc">
	<div class="large-3 columns">
		<h2>Marketing Collateral</h2>
		<div class="productBoxImg"><%= image_tag("brochure.jpg") %></div>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<div class="prodDescBox">
			<p>Even in an increasingly online world, buyers of big ticket items expect the high-quality imagery and detailed information that only paper can provide. Whether you sell real estate, medical services, furniture or business services, Color Craze can produce impactful collateral that will help you close sales.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Formats include fliers, brochures, booklets, posters, notecards and letterhead </li>
				<li>Sizes up to 11" x 17"</li>
				<li>Matte to glossy finish</li>
				<li>Lots sizes from 100 to 2,500</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="thinSpacerRow"></div>
<div class="row prodDesc">
	<div class="large-3 columns">
		<h2>Direct Mail</h2>
		<div class="productBoxImg"><%= image_tag("direct_mail.jpg") %></div>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<div class="prodDescBox">
			<p>Get around email inbox clutter and spam filters with old-fashioned, but effective, paper mail. We offer full service direct mail services for small (&lt10,000 pieces) mailings, including printing, stuffing and mailing.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Postcards, business-sized or irregular envelopes</li>
				<li>Cardstock or paper</li>
				<li>Color or black and white</li>
				<li>Mailings from from 100 to 2,500 pieces</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="thinSpacerRow"></div>
<div class="row prodDesc">
	<div class="large-3 columns">
		<h2>Other Business Services</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<div class="prodDescBox">
			<p>Items we print are limited only by your imagination. Other examples of work we have done for clients includes directories, programs, tickets for events, multi-part forms, coloring pages, planograms, manuals, bookmarks and product labels.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="thinSpacerRow"></div>
<div class="row prodDesc">
	<div class="large-3 columns">
		<h2>Other Personal Services</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="large-9 columns">
		<div class="prodDescBox">
			<p>We also routinely print for individuals as well. Items include invitations, holiday cards, calendars, personalized letterhead, etc.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
